{"utt_id": "en_174-168635-0000", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/174/168635/174-168635-0000.wav", "ref_text": "HE HAD NEVER BEEN FATHER LOVER HUSBAND FRIEND", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "17eaa64a47d8ec140e70bcc7b26e3fe5", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 4.53, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_174-168635-0001", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/174/168635/174-168635-0001.wav", "ref_text": "THE HEART OF THAT EX CONVICT WAS FULL OF VIRGINITY", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "0fc86aa1427bace5f8b77dfb356ef072", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 4.65, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_174-168635-0002", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/174/168635/174-168635-0002.wav", "ref_text": "HIS SISTER AND HIS SISTER'S CHILDREN HAD LEFT HIM ONLY A VAGUE AND FAR OFF MEMORY WHICH HAD FINALLY ALMOST COMPLETELY VANISHED HE HAD MADE EVERY EFFORT TO FIND THEM AND NOT HAVING BEEN ABLE TO FIND THEM HE HAD FORGOTTEN THEM", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "1f1f6bb0ff7e5a0f3ee43ec07a7c7f49", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 15.86, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_174-168635-0003", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/174/168635/174-168635-0003.wav", "ref_text": "HE SUFFERED ALL THE PANGS OF A MOTHER AND HE KNEW NOT WHAT IT MEANT FOR THAT GREAT AND SINGULAR MOVEMENT OF A HEART WHICH BEGINS TO LOVE IS A VERY OBSCURE AND A VERY SWEET THING", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "230c5a26b5acd8853228e202f7bfe86d", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 13.18, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_174-168635-0004", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/174/168635/174-168635-0004.wav", "ref_text": "ONLY AS HE WAS FIVE AND FIFTY AND COSETTE EIGHT YEARS OF AGE ALL THAT MIGHT HAVE BEEN LOVE IN THE WHOLE COURSE OF HIS LIFE FLOWED TOGETHER INTO A SORT OF INEFFABLE LIGHT", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "964dfdabc5e78b8778b0aa6443dc2425", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 12.77, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_174-168635-0005", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/174/168635/174-168635-0005.wav", "ref_text": "COSETTE ON HER SIDE HAD ALSO UNKNOWN TO HERSELF BECOME ANOTHER BEING POOR LITTLE THING", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "2da8b376ce66634d00235363602c74ad", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 7.93, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_174-168635-0006", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/174/168635/174-168635-0006.wav", "ref_text": "SHE FELT THAT WHICH SHE HAD NEVER FELT BEFORE A SENSATION OF EXPANSION", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "a60e3ad225de9fadd4647d7013c947d2", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 6.57, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_174-168635-0007", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/174/168635/174-168635-0007.wav", "ref_text": "THE MAN NO LONGER PRODUCED ON HER THE EFFECT OF BEING OLD OR POOR SHE THOUGHT JEAN VALJEAN HANDSOME JUST AS SHE THOUGHT THE HOVEL PRETTY", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "81b628bfb23bc95085bc3060cf6e3637", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 10.21, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_174-168635-0008", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/174/168635/174-168635-0008.wav", "ref_text": "NATURE A DIFFERENCE OF FIFTY YEARS HAD SET A PROFOUND GULF BETWEEN JEAN VALJEAN AND COSETTE DESTINY FILLED IN THIS GULF", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "f0b8e2982b97384b54c9bea1287273b0", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 10.235, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_174-168635-0009", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/174/168635/174-168635-0009.wav", "ref_text": "TO MEET WAS TO FIND EACH OTHER", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "e4586e2064c4f3272ea1761e92dc510f", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 3.28, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_174-168635-0010", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/174/168635/174-168635-0010.wav", "ref_text": "WHEN THESE TWO SOULS PERCEIVED EACH OTHER THEY RECOGNIZED EACH OTHER AS NECESSARY TO EACH OTHER AND EMBRACED EACH OTHER CLOSELY", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "c8599a01200f7a66f6a3a466d068e378", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 10.06, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_174-168635-0011", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/174/168635/174-168635-0011.wav", "ref_text": "MOREOVER JEAN VALJEAN HAD CHOSEN HIS REFUGE WELL", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "4a8e88bfc37b61e0de24f41b38a94d6a", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 4.645, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_174-168635-0012", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/174/168635/174-168635-0012.wav", "ref_text": "HE HAD PAID HER SIX MONTHS IN ADVANCE AND HAD COMMISSIONED THE OLD WOMAN TO FURNISH THE CHAMBER AND DRESSING ROOM AS WE HAVE SEEN", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "a0ddd8cb818653bb81c9f1e3cbc1c3aa", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 8.36, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_174-168635-0013", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/174/168635/174-168635-0013.wav", "ref_text": "WEEK FOLLOWED WEEK THESE TWO BEINGS LED A HAPPY LIFE IN THAT HOVEL", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "dcb3bfece21fffc92921125a31e2977e", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 5.87, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_174-168635-0014", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/174/168635/174-168635-0014.wav", "ref_text": "COSETTE WAS NO LONGER IN RAGS SHE WAS IN MOURNING", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "58afe1616940ea323bd21082eace56b2", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 4.8251, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_174-168635-0015", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/174/168635/174-168635-0015.wav", "ref_text": "AND THEN HE TALKED OF HER MOTHER AND HE MADE HER PRAY", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "d9b31eef17f7841effa65d787e12a60e", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 4.19, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_174-168635-0016", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/174/168635/174-168635-0016.wav", "ref_text": "HE PASSED HOURS IN WATCHING HER DRESSING AND UNDRESSING HER DOLL AND IN LISTENING TO HER PRATTLE", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "4ebe0d697ad76f71c937d0c97d8bc672", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 7.06, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_174-168635-0017", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/174/168635/174-168635-0017.wav", "ref_text": "THE BEST OF US ARE NOT EXEMPT FROM EGOTISTICAL THOUGHTS", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "8de6b78b697eaf2500dc8c32c8cd2499", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 4.57, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_174-168635-0018", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/174/168635/174-168635-0018.wav", "ref_text": "HE HAD RETURNED TO PRISON THIS TIME FOR HAVING DONE RIGHT HE HAD QUAFFED FRESH BITTERNESS DISGUST AND LASSITUDE WERE OVERPOWERING HIM EVEN THE MEMORY OF THE BISHOP PROBABLY SUFFERED A TEMPORARY ECLIPSE THOUGH SURE TO REAPPEAR LATER ON LUMINOUS AND TRIUMPHANT BUT AFTER ALL THAT SACRED MEMORY WAS GROWING DIM", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "1fa24a0e680432f6303e348efae2f040", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 27.11, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_174-168635-0019", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/174/168635/174-168635-0019.wav", "ref_text": "WHO KNOWS WHETHER JEAN VALJEAN HAD NOT BEEN ON THE EVE OF GROWING DISCOURAGED AND OF FALLING ONCE MORE", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "39b152ba12aae7ecb2eab70aed3be718", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 8.0, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_174-168635-0020", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/174/168635/174-168635-0020.wav", "ref_text": "ALAS HE WALKED WITH NO LESS INDECISION THAN COSETTE", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "726ab480d07c3fc99d8772072e6dde4d", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 4.62, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_174-168635-0021", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/174/168635/174-168635-0021.wav", "ref_text": "HE PROTECTED HER AND SHE STRENGTHENED HIM", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "738c92dca157ca0906820b8d67e41182", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 4.17, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_174-168635-0022", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/174/168635/174-168635-0022.wav", "ref_text": "HE WAS THAT CHILD'S STAY AND SHE WAS HIS PROP", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "a00f27b85eb4d1ca29782fc9536ec295", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 4.335, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_174-50561-0000", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/174/50561/174-50561-0000.wav", "ref_text": "FORGOTTEN TOO THE NAME OF GILLIAN THE LOVELY CAPTIVE", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "f30c87f1bac5824e524581bfaa8f768c", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 4.02, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_174-50561-0001", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/174/50561/174-50561-0001.wav", "ref_text": "WORSE AND WORSE HE IS EVEN PRESUMED TO BE THE CAPTIVE'S SWEETHEART WHO WHEEDLES THE FLOWER THE RING AND THE PRISON KEY OUT OF THE STRICT VIRGINS FOR HIS OWN PURPOSES AND FLIES WITH HER AT LAST IN HIS SHALLOP ACROSS THE SEA TO LIVE WITH HER HAPPILY EVER AFTER", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "1410a3665beeea550cda8b6f02dca667", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 15.86, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_174-50561-0002", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/174/50561/174-50561-0002.wav", "ref_text": "BUT THIS IS A FALLACY", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "b975150aa599fcbdbabb41fe8fec17ec", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 2.145, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_174-50561-0003", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/174/50561/174-50561-0003.wav", "ref_text": "THE WANDERING SINGER APPROACHES THEM WITH HIS LUTE", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "8693aae5a199541a41a7631762ce490f", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 3.34, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_174-50561-0004", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/174/50561/174-50561-0004.wav", "ref_text": "THE EMPEROR'S DAUGHTER", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "c0bf82355a3e51b8da0ccb25ea8ae8dd", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 2.06, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_174-50561-0005", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/174/50561/174-50561-0005.wav", "ref_text": "LADY LADY MY ROSE WHITE LADY BUT WILL YOU NOT HEAR A ROUNDEL LADY", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "8ddb15b2b9089321b4f9ce500d851d53", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 5.705, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_174-50561-0006", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/174/50561/174-50561-0006.wav", "ref_text": "O IF YOU PLAY US A ROUNDEL SINGER HOW CAN THAT HARM THE EMPEROR'S DAUGHTER", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "5ce8f549506cc30df91363092b15249f", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 5.215, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_174-50561-0007", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/174/50561/174-50561-0007.wav", "ref_text": "SHE WOULD NOT SPEAK THOUGH WE DANCED A WEEK WITH HER THOUGHTS A THOUSAND LEAGUES OVER THE WATER SINGER SINGER WANDERING SINGER O MY HONEY SWEET SINGER", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "a723c8d06c7fcf172154b90a80018d8c", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 10.855, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_174-50561-0008", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/174/50561/174-50561-0008.wav", "ref_text": "BUT IF I PLAY YOU A ROUNDEL LADY GET ME A GIFT FROM THE EMPEROR'S DAUGHTER HER FINGER RING FOR MY FINGER BRING THOUGH SHE'S PLEDGED A THOUSAND LEAGUES OVER THE WATER LADY LADY MY FAIR LADY O MY ROSE WHITE LADY", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "5f8546de68b51174e48208bb2682790d", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 16.31, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_174-50561-0009", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/174/50561/174-50561-0009.wav", "ref_text": "THE WANDERING SINGER", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "1a7904e3f0c63309604b5b1aaa6c39ab", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 2.04, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_174-50561-0010", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/174/50561/174-50561-0010.wav", "ref_text": "BUT I DID ONCE HAVE THE LUCK TO HEAR AND SEE THE LADY PLAYED IN ENTIRETY THE CHILDREN HAD BEEN GRANTED LEAVE TO PLAY JUST ONE MORE GAME BEFORE BED TIME AND OF COURSE THEY CHOSE THE LONGEST AND PLAYED IT WITHOUT MISSING A SYLLABLE", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "0be7fecf0b394ae02feb55f2c100fcc8", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 14.91, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_174-50561-0011", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/174/50561/174-50561-0011.wav", "ref_text": "THE LADIES IN YELLOW DRESSES STAND AGAIN IN A RING ABOUT THE EMPEROR'S DAUGHTER AND ARE FOR THE LAST TIME ACCOSTED BY THE SINGER WITH HIS LUTE", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "a3cda8eefa5501a21698de890e1ca925", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 9.52, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_174-50561-0012", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/174/50561/174-50561-0012.wav", "ref_text": "THE WANDERING SINGER", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "bcada48579b91dde2360a3b0b7598cbe", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 2.07, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_174-50561-0013", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/174/50561/174-50561-0013.wav", "ref_text": "I'LL PLAY FOR YOU NOW NEATH THE APPLE BOUGH AND YOU SHALL DREAM ON THE LAWN SO SHADY LADY LADY MY FAIR LADY O MY APPLE GOLD LADY", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "aef1de6888b0ad684bec3a072f1489d3", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 10.615, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_174-50561-0014", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/174/50561/174-50561-0014.wav", "ref_text": "THE LADIES", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "e7fca1d0cf2ff7c380b6947f9e5d4422", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 1.8, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_174-50561-0015", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/174/50561/174-50561-0015.wav", "ref_text": "NOW YOU MAY PLAY A SERENA SINGER A DREAM OF NIGHT FOR AN APPLE GOLD LADY FOR THE FRUIT IS NOW ON THE APPLE BOUGH AND THE MOON IS UP AND THE LAWN IS SHADY SINGER SINGER WANDERING SINGER O MY HONEY SWEET SINGER", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "3c8c2518596fb46bfe8a5d4166211ec2", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 16.76, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_174-50561-0016", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/174/50561/174-50561-0016.wav", "ref_text": "ONCE MORE THE SINGER PLAYS AND THE LADIES DANCE BUT ONE BY ONE THEY FALL ASLEEP TO THE DROWSY MUSIC AND THEN THE SINGER STEPS INTO THE RING AND UNLOCKS THE TOWER AND KISSES THE EMPEROR'S DAUGHTER", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "155b2ac6d8548b0e3b5a6b74f51b7b6b", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 13.455, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_174-50561-0017", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/174/50561/174-50561-0017.wav", "ref_text": "I DON'T KNOW WHAT BECOMES OF THE LADIES", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "0104321e3f2beed9e9555369df2fd8ee", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 2.825, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_174-50561-0018", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/174/50561/174-50561-0018.wav", "ref_text": "BED TIME CHILDREN", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "869f34eaaf6312445c0b816f134bb5da", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 2.12, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_174-50561-0019", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/174/50561/174-50561-0019.wav", "ref_text": "YOU SEE THE TREATMENT IS A TRIFLE FANCIFUL", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "8f1a7accc0b6cb13ef96b1a20bcddf92", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 4.26, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_174-84280-0000", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/174/84280/174-84280-0000.wav", "ref_text": "HOW WE MUST SIMPLIFY", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "5a9d0e96de900c20ee5f07eea98c12bb", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 2.4, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_174-84280-0001", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/174/84280/174-84280-0001.wav", "ref_text": "IT SEEMS TO ME MORE AND MORE AS I LIVE LONGER THAT MOST POETRY AND MOST LITERATURE AND PARTICULARLY THE LITERATURE OF THE PAST IS DISCORDANT WITH THE VASTNESS AND VARIETY THE RESERVES AND RESOURCES AND RECUPERATIONS OF LIFE AS WE LIVE IT TO DAY", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "73628bd2854e034b5b66accf036a6b10", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 18.33, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_174-84280-0002", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/174/84280/174-84280-0002.wav", "ref_text": "IT IS THE EXPRESSION OF LIFE UNDER CRUDER AND MORE RIGID CONDITIONS THAN OURS LIVED BY PEOPLE WHO LOVED AND HATED MORE NAIVELY AGED SOONER AND DIED YOUNGER THAN WE DO", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "39e3f756834c7142e1193fadf6a5ce6b", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 12.2, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_174-84280-0003", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/174/84280/174-84280-0003.wav", "ref_text": "WE RANGE WIDER LAST LONGER AND ESCAPE MORE AND MORE FROM INTENSITY TOWARDS UNDERSTANDING", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "f02260cee3c4cf537e64853aadce5a28", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 7.445, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_174-84280-0004", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/174/84280/174-84280-0004.wav", "ref_text": "AND ALREADY THIS ASTOUNDING BLOW BEGINS TO TAKE ITS PLACE AMONG OTHER EVENTS AS A THING STRANGE AND TERRIBLE INDEED BUT RELATED TO ALL THE STRANGENESS AND MYSTERY OF LIFE PART OF THE UNIVERSAL MYSTERIES OF DESPAIR AND FUTILITY AND DEATH THAT HAVE TROUBLED MY CONSCIOUSNESS SINCE CHILDHOOD", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "9872bf4427358a9aad0b0a521c821dfb", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 20.53, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_174-84280-0005", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/174/84280/174-84280-0005.wav", "ref_text": "FOR A TIME THE DEATH OF MARY OBSCURED HER LIFE FOR ME BUT NOW HER LIVING PRESENCE IS MORE IN MY MIND AGAIN", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "9635bc78c2e2989d9e2efa7af87fc58d", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 8.61, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_174-84280-0006", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/174/84280/174-84280-0006.wav", "ref_text": "IT WAS THAT IDEA OF WASTE THAT DOMINATED MY MIND IN A STRANGE INTERVIEW I HAD WITH JUSTIN", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "f7a5a7cb5cc97737797b9204308e15ca", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 7.03, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_174-84280-0007", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/174/84280/174-84280-0007.wav", "ref_text": "I BECAME GROTESQUELY ANXIOUS TO ASSURE HIM THAT INDEED SHE AND I HAD BEEN AS THEY SAY INNOCENT THROUGHOUT OUR LAST DAY TOGETHER", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "0de634ce1dc93e950fa78ed4ffbd9cb1", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 9.73, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_174-84280-0008", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/174/84280/174-84280-0008.wav", "ref_text": "YOU WERE WRONG IN ALL THAT I SAID SHE KEPT HER FAITH WITH YOU", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "c40308e1abbc2482331625e6053944a3", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 4.52, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_174-84280-0009", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/174/84280/174-84280-0009.wav", "ref_text": "WE NEVER PLANNED TO MEET AND WHEN WE MET", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "a6067a2995701b9bba66ab22d072e803", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 3.1, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_174-84280-0010", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/174/84280/174-84280-0010.wav", "ref_text": "IF WE HAD BEEN BROTHER AND SISTER INDEED THERE WAS NOTHING", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "21c7e05a5c32e7de3788b8b3940b5c98", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 4.36, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_174-84280-0011", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/174/84280/174-84280-0011.wav", "ref_text": "BUT NOW IT DOESN'T SEEM TO MATTER VERY MUCH", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "39684425803dfaba525c74451a556432", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 3.355, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_174-84280-0012", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/174/84280/174-84280-0012.wav", "ref_text": "AND IT IS UPON THIS EFFECT OF SWEET AND BEAUTIFUL POSSIBILITIES CAUGHT IN THE NET OF ANIMAL JEALOUSIES AND THOUGHTLESS MOTIVES AND ANCIENT RIGID INSTITUTIONS THAT I WOULD END THIS WRITING", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "a77005f5bf230299db2a2be1efbff899", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 14.43, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_174-84280-0013", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/174/84280/174-84280-0013.wav", "ref_text": "IN MARY IT SEEMS TO ME I FOUND BOTH WOMANHOOD AND FELLOWSHIP I FOUND WHAT MANY HAVE DREAMT OF LOVE AND FRIENDSHIP FREELY GIVEN AND I COULD DO NOTHING BUT CLUTCH AT HER TO MAKE HER MY POSSESSION", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "f987c3826e736ea75f3dff37f12713f5", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 16.86, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_174-84280-0014", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/174/84280/174-84280-0014.wav", "ref_text": "WHAT ALTERNATIVE WAS THERE FOR HER", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "8a99f37eac17e12ec25fb67dc90fe42e", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 3.0101, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_174-84280-0015", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/174/84280/174-84280-0015.wav", "ref_text": "SHE WAS DESTROYED NOT MERELY BY THE UNCONSIDERED UNDISCIPLINED PASSIONS OF HER HUSBAND AND HER LOVER BUT BY THE VAST TRADITION THAT SUSTAINS AND ENFORCES THE SUBJUGATION OF HER SEX", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "4d5f9fb09a6d751b837448b3b21c38c4", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 13.73, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_84-121123-0000", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/84/121123/84-121123-0000.wav", "ref_text": "GO DO YOU HEAR", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "700c770a5974bc1f8a35b0c6f5284085", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 2.09, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_84-121123-0001", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/84/121123/84-121123-0001.wav", "ref_text": "BUT IN LESS THAN FIVE MINUTES THE STAIRCASE GROANED BENEATH AN EXTRAORDINARY WEIGHT", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "f033fcdaddf39bf1db95de9f1fde57e4", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 3.99, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_84-121123-0002", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/84/121123/84-121123-0002.wav", "ref_text": "AT THIS MOMENT THE WHOLE SOUL OF THE OLD MAN SEEMED CENTRED IN HIS EYES WHICH BECAME BLOODSHOT THE VEINS OF THE THROAT SWELLED HIS CHEEKS AND TEMPLES BECAME PURPLE AS THOUGH HE WAS STRUCK WITH EPILEPSY NOTHING WAS WANTING TO COMPLETE THIS BUT THE UTTERANCE OF A CRY", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "7086c5ef9b7edbf638bd073bd86a6bfb", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 13.69, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_84-121123-0003", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/84/121123/84-121123-0003.wav", "ref_text": "AND THE CRY ISSUED FROM HIS PORES IF WE MAY THUS SPEAK A CRY FRIGHTFUL IN ITS SILENCE", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "3878255e90561dc1c711637a3bbf580b", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 6.8, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_84-121123-0004", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/84/121123/84-121123-0004.wav", "ref_text": "D'AVRIGNY RUSHED TOWARDS THE OLD MAN AND MADE HIM INHALE A POWERFUL RESTORATIVE", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "2296c6b8fb3355d1424ec560d3c7a4fe", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 4.4, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_84-121123-0005", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/84/121123/84-121123-0005.wav", "ref_text": "D'AVRIGNY UNABLE TO BEAR THE SIGHT OF THIS TOUCHING EMOTION TURNED AWAY AND VILLEFORT WITHOUT SEEKING ANY FURTHER EXPLANATION AND ATTRACTED TOWARDS HIM BY THE IRRESISTIBLE MAGNETISM WHICH DRAWS US TOWARDS THOSE WHO HAVE LOVED THE PEOPLE FOR WHOM WE MOURN EXTENDED HIS HAND TOWARDS THE YOUNG MAN", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "1cff70245691171ef629f36b18a95c22", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 15.96, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_84-121123-0006", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/84/121123/84-121123-0006.wav", "ref_text": "FOR SOME TIME NOTHING WAS HEARD IN THAT CHAMBER BUT SOBS EXCLAMATIONS AND PRAYERS", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "a6f8796f65c95c3ba35055d59da98123", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 5.62, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_84-121123-0007", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/84/121123/84-121123-0007.wav", "ref_text": "WHAT DO YOU MEAN SIR", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "e2c68ac002f3924d70d1aec473b114f5", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 2.0, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_84-121123-0008", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/84/121123/84-121123-0008.wav", "ref_text": "OH YOU RAVE SIR EXCLAIMED VILLEFORT IN VAIN ENDEAVORING TO ESCAPE THE NET IN WHICH HE WAS TAKEN I RAVE", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "126e5e3aa696eb383fcddc4305f8c852", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 7.015, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_84-121123-0009", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/84/121123/84-121123-0009.wav", "ref_text": "DO YOU KNOW THE ASSASSIN ASKED MORREL", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "9d6597b279b71872e786bfa5379d4440", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 2.6951, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_84-121123-0010", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/84/121123/84-121123-0010.wav", "ref_text": "NOIRTIER LOOKED UPON MORREL WITH ONE OF THOSE MELANCHOLY SMILES WHICH HAD SO OFTEN MADE VALENTINE HAPPY AND THUS FIXED HIS ATTENTION", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "4e0a866cfd019a148b541a37fffd1155", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 7.19, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_84-121123-0011", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/84/121123/84-121123-0011.wav", "ref_text": "SAID MORREL SADLY YES REPLIED NOIRTIER", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "32a5f1d9cd8dbcfd1fb50e6f85adc5ac", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 3.25, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_84-121123-0012", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/84/121123/84-121123-0012.wav", "ref_text": "THE OLD MAN'S EYES REMAINED FIXED ON THE DOOR", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "8703472adc170c41f7570bd7953bff01", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 2.56, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_84-121123-0013", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/84/121123/84-121123-0013.wav", "ref_text": "ASKED MORREL YES", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "dac2b13a0fc26eab9d50bd18a99c42eb", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 2.4, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_84-121123-0014", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/84/121123/84-121123-0014.wav", "ref_text": "MUST I LEAVE ALONE NO", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "4ad7dfe83c517cc9b92be3d94689bac9", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 2.885, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_84-121123-0015", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/84/121123/84-121123-0015.wav", "ref_text": "BUT CAN HE UNDERSTAND YOU YES", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "1e90b464f3b0fb52b7a3be12b1da3be3", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 3.035, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_84-121123-0016", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/84/121123/84-121123-0016.wav", "ref_text": "GENTLEMEN HE SAID IN A HOARSE VOICE GIVE ME YOUR WORD OF HONOR THAT THIS HORRIBLE SECRET SHALL FOREVER REMAIN BURIED AMONGST OURSELVES THE TWO MEN DREW BACK", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "059f9b0ff9028cda50d93c14f8796277", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 8.41, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_84-121123-0017", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/84/121123/84-121123-0017.wav", "ref_text": "MY FATHER HAS REVEALED THE CULPRIT'S NAME MY FATHER THIRSTS FOR REVENGE AS MUCH AS YOU DO YET EVEN HE CONJURES YOU AS I DO TO KEEP THIS SECRET DO YOU NOT FATHER", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "b9d32f86f545d831cbd3b96fa0a90fcf", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 9.375, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_84-121123-0018", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/84/121123/84-121123-0018.wav", "ref_text": "MORREL SUFFERED AN EXCLAMATION OF HORROR AND SURPRISE TO ESCAPE HIM", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "fb7d2e7b5d88b4215a4055c1b884e959", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 3.55, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_84-121123-0019", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/84/121123/84-121123-0019.wav", "ref_text": "THE OLD MAN MADE A SIGN IN THE AFFIRMATIVE", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "225a9e12ce448dff851078766cc02442", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 2.435, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_84-121123-0020", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/84/121123/84-121123-0020.wav", "ref_text": "IT WAS SOMETHING TERRIBLE TO WITNESS THE SILENT AGONY THE MUTE DESPAIR OF NOIRTIER WHOSE TEARS SILENTLY ROLLED DOWN HIS CHEEKS", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "a84d94aa51031b57d74742cf4a245481", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 6.92, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_84-121123-0021", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/84/121123/84-121123-0021.wav", "ref_text": "BUT HE STOPPED ON THE LANDING HE HAD NOT THE COURAGE TO AGAIN VISIT THE DEATH CHAMBER", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "f5e94499ed091c243632e08dfc1874f0", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 4.815, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_84-121123-0022", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/84/121123/84-121123-0022.wav", "ref_text": "THE TWO DOCTORS THEREFORE ENTERED THE ROOM ALONE", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "bef30396349b593bf78de028632987a8", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 2.61, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_84-121123-0023", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/84/121123/84-121123-0023.wav", "ref_text": "NOIRTIER WAS NEAR THE BED PALE MOTIONLESS AND SILENT AS THE CORPSE", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "59df286b99115991f1397152c24ecf2e", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 4.685, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_84-121123-0024", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/84/121123/84-121123-0024.wav", "ref_text": "THE DISTRICT DOCTOR APPROACHED WITH THE INDIFFERENCE OF A MAN ACCUSTOMED TO SPEND HALF HIS TIME AMONGST THE DEAD HE THEN LIFTED THE SHEET WHICH WAS PLACED OVER THE FACE AND JUST UNCLOSED THE LIPS", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "bdfb12c2fad729edb6cde5f5e9c90350", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 10.38, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_84-121123-0025", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/84/121123/84-121123-0025.wav", "ref_text": "THE NEAREST SAID THE DISTRICT DOCTOR IS A GOOD ITALIAN ABBE WHO LIVES NEXT DOOR TO YOU SHALL I CALL ON HIM AS I PASS", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "54480939d58dc2d7328fe72dcf4c253b", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 6.255, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_84-121123-0026", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/84/121123/84-121123-0026.wav", "ref_text": "D'AVRIGNY SAID VILLEFORT BE SO KIND I BESEECH YOU AS TO ACCOMPANY THIS GENTLEMAN HERE IS THE KEY OF THE DOOR SO THAT YOU CAN GO IN AND OUT AS YOU PLEASE YOU WILL BRING THE PRIEST WITH YOU AND WILL OBLIGE ME BY INTRODUCING HIM INTO MY CHILD'S ROOM DO YOU WISH TO SEE HIM", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "952c2746a29789c62c79dcb0ba824cdf", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 13.94, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_84-121123-0027", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/84/121123/84-121123-0027.wav", "ref_text": "I ONLY WISH TO BE ALONE YOU WILL EXCUSE ME WILL YOU NOT", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "2943320efca0aaae66503761f4ef266f", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 3.07, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_84-121123-0028", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/84/121123/84-121123-0028.wav", "ref_text": "I AM GOING SIR AND I DO NOT HESITATE TO SAY THAT NO PRAYERS WILL BE MORE FERVENT THAN MINE", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "e00977d89dd0e7db6b85928b4e995b90", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 4.76, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_84-121550-0000", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/84/121550/84-121550-0000.wav", "ref_text": "BUT WITH FULL RAVISHMENT THE HOURS OF PRIME SINGING RECEIVED THEY IN THE MIDST OF LEAVES THAT EVER BORE A BURDEN TO THEIR RHYMES", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "a9df4af58bcc2578aecfc3ad83f8956f", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 8.435, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_84-121550-0001", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/84/121550/84-121550-0001.wav", "ref_text": "ALL WATERS THAT ON EARTH MOST LIMPID ARE WOULD SEEM TO HAVE WITHIN THEMSELVES SOME MIXTURE COMPARED WITH THAT WHICH NOTHING DOTH CONCEAL", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "242ea3f2ca6839241d7e7a8df58d44e4", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 7.975, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_84-121550-0002", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/84/121550/84-121550-0002.wav", "ref_text": "THOU MAKEST ME REMEMBER WHERE AND WHAT PROSERPINA THAT MOMENT WAS WHEN LOST HER MOTHER HER AND SHE HERSELF THE SPRING", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "cbd08dd5ab45a7a58a1ed01c03598de1", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 8.265, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_84-121550-0003", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/84/121550/84-121550-0003.wav", "ref_text": "I DO NOT THINK THERE SHONE SO GREAT A LIGHT UNDER THE LIDS OF VENUS WHEN TRANSFIXED BY HER OWN SON BEYOND HIS USUAL CUSTOM", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "622e12515c84bfaf7130d1bd20e8590c", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 8.16, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_84-121550-0004", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/84/121550/84-121550-0004.wav", "ref_text": "YE ARE NEW COMERS AND BECAUSE I SMILE BEGAN SHE PERADVENTURE IN THIS PLACE ELECT TO HUMAN NATURE FOR ITS NEST", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "985e2dc7683e62ccf9bc7b0019f877da", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 7.965, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_84-121550-0005", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/84/121550/84-121550-0005.wav", "ref_text": "SOME APPREHENSION KEEPS YOU MARVELLING BUT THE PSALM DELECTASTI GIVETH LIGHT WHICH HAS THE POWER TO UNCLOUD YOUR INTELLECT", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "466e1e80307eefc70297331c16bb25ee", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 8.7149, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_84-121550-0006", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/84/121550/84-121550-0006.wav", "ref_text": "THE GOOD SUPREME SOLE IN ITSELF DELIGHTING CREATED MAN GOOD AND THIS GOODLY PLACE GAVE HIM AS HANSEL OF ETERNAL PEACE", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "13c46e3eb7be3202c4ceb548b9876842", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 8.83, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_84-121550-0007", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/84/121550/84-121550-0007.wav", "ref_text": "BY HIS DEFAULT SHORT WHILE HE SOJOURNED HERE BY HIS DEFAULT TO WEEPING AND TO TOIL HE CHANGED HIS INNOCENT LAUGHTER AND SWEET PLAY", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "6968fc94a158c149caba3d56432b7e34", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 9.525, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_84-121550-0008", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/84/121550/84-121550-0008.wav", "ref_text": "THIS EVERY OTHER SAVOUR DOTH TRANSCEND AND NOTWITHSTANDING SLAKED SO FAR MAY BE THY THIRST THAT I REVEAL TO THEE NO MORE", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "cc91768508213f4031ba3b654db6d927", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 8.445, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_84-121550-0009", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/84/121550/84-121550-0009.wav", "ref_text": "BETWEEN HER STEPS AND MINE WERE NOT A HUNDRED WHEN EQUALLY THE MARGINS GAVE A TURN IN SUCH A WAY THAT TO THE EAST I FACED", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "5c70865df9c4303348bee955412cc509", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 8.615, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_84-121550-0010", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/84/121550/84-121550-0010.wav", "ref_text": "NOR EVEN THUS OUR WAY CONTINUED FAR BEFORE THE LADY WHOLLY TURNED HERSELF UNTO ME SAYING BROTHER LOOK AND LISTEN", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "cfc23b7c9ea73a4ced874e3ac0d542ed", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 8.33, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_84-121550-0011", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/84/121550/84-121550-0011.wav", "ref_text": "NOW HELICON MUST NEEDS POUR FORTH FOR ME AND WITH HER CHOIR URANIA MUST ASSIST ME TO PUT IN VERSE THINGS DIFFICULT TO THINK", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "f91e65390afd8be35b2f8b83f30176f0", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 9.355, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_84-121550-0012", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/84/121550/84-121550-0012.wav", "ref_text": "THEN BACK I TURNED MY FACE TO THOSE HIGH THINGS WHICH MOVED THEMSELVES TOWARDS US SO SEDATELY THEY HAD BEEN DISTANCED BY NEW WEDDED BRIDES", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "11adfbba3009f485537fec4f789cffd4", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 9.24, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_84-121550-0013", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/84/121550/84-121550-0013.wav", "ref_text": "AND I BEHELD THE FLAMELETS ONWARD GO LEAVING BEHIND THEMSELVES THE AIR DEPICTED AND THEY OF TRAILING PENNONS HAD THE SEMBLANCE SO THAT IT OVERHEAD REMAINED DISTINCT WITH SEVENFOLD LISTS ALL OF THEM OF THE COLOURS WHENCE THE SUN'S BOW IS MADE AND DELIA'S GIRDLE", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "eeec207824716f5723a67e58d55ff86f", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 19.11, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_84-121550-0014", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/84/121550/84-121550-0014.wav", "ref_text": "THESE STANDARDS TO THE REARWARD LONGER WERE THAN WAS MY SIGHT AND AS IT SEEMED TO ME TEN PACES WERE THE OUTERMOST APART", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "5a047a9b54817a155c8e8e14f28ee6ea", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 8.185, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_84-121550-0015", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/84/121550/84-121550-0015.wav", "ref_text": "THE INTERVAL BETWEEN THESE FOUR CONTAINED A CHARIOT TRIUMPHAL ON TWO WHEELS WHICH BY A GRIFFIN'S NECK CAME DRAWN ALONG", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "92bbcec61a1e16b6caf5b078b675f2bb", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 8.155, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_84-121550-0016", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/84/121550/84-121550-0016.wav", "ref_text": "NOT ONLY ROME WITH NO SUCH SPLENDID CAR E'ER GLADDENED AFRICANUS OR AUGUSTUS BUT POOR TO IT THAT OF THE SUN WOULD BE", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "3a7601ddef538356a00dacfc4ffbd0a5", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 8.955, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_84-121550-0017", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/84/121550/84-121550-0017.wav", "ref_text": "THREE MAIDENS AT THE RIGHT WHEEL IN A CIRCLE CAME ONWARD DANCING ONE SO VERY RED THAT IN THE FIRE SHE HARDLY HAD BEEN NOTED", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "2e76ed42ea2d4d7586f1949c8b1fb19f", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 8.645, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_84-121550-0018", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/84/121550/84-121550-0018.wav", "ref_text": "THE SECOND WAS AS IF HER FLESH AND BONES HAD ALL BEEN FASHIONED OUT OF EMERALD THE THIRD APPEARED AS SNOW BUT NEWLY FALLEN", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "c9ae7225e9f947d7b658572c6b2e20f3", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 9.46, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_84-121550-0019", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/84/121550/84-121550-0019.wav", "ref_text": "IN REAR OF ALL THE GROUP HERE TREATED OF TWO OLD MEN I BEHELD UNLIKE IN HABIT BUT LIKE IN GAIT EACH DIGNIFIED AND GRAVE", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "bd634f19625c0f5575f99fb81b11403e", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 9.2799, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_84-121550-0020", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/84/121550/84-121550-0020.wav", "ref_text": "AND WHEN THE CAR WAS OPPOSITE TO ME THUNDER WAS HEARD AND ALL THAT FOLK AUGUST SEEMED TO HAVE FURTHER PROGRESS INTERDICTED", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "912513b5538bc1187220e63f945f1db2", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 8.39, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_84-121550-0021", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/84/121550/84-121550-0021.wav", "ref_text": "AND ONE OF THEM AS IF BY HEAVEN COMMISSIONED SINGING VENI SPONSA DE LIBANO SHOUTED THREE TIMES AND ALL THE OTHERS AFTER", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "27301746af7749b4d36d6196381b86ec", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 8.71, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_84-121550-0022", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/84/121550/84-121550-0022.wav", "ref_text": "AS SOON AS ON MY VISION SMOTE THE POWER SUBLIME THAT HAD ALREADY PIERCED ME THROUGH ERE FROM MY BOYHOOD I HAD YET COME FORTH", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "250c759cc3bd4097b2c6ea43c273184d", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 7.65, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_84-121550-0023", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/84/121550/84-121550-0023.wav", "ref_text": "TO THE LEFT HAND I TURNED WITH THAT RELIANCE WITH WHICH THE LITTLE CHILD RUNS TO HIS MOTHER WHEN HE HAS FEAR OR WHEN HE IS AFFLICTED", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "8f868e92546e408daae6fa8b77225254", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 7.215, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_84-121550-0024", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/84/121550/84-121550-0024.wav", "ref_text": "TO SAY UNTO VIRGILIUS NOT A DRACHM OF BLOOD REMAINS IN ME THAT DOES NOT TREMBLE I KNOW THE TRACES OF THE ANCIENT FLAME", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "0fa08bc62b8e52bb0288a8f7cb491629", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 8.63, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_84-121550-0025", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/84/121550/84-121550-0025.wav", "ref_text": "DANTE BECAUSE VIRGILIUS HAS DEPARTED DO NOT WEEP YET DO NOT WEEP YET AWHILE FOR BY ANOTHER SWORD THOU NEED'ST MUST WEEP", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "74b9d55f33bbdc80a9115563d6e74394", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 9.84, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_84-121550-0026", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/84/121550/84-121550-0026.wav", "ref_text": "I SAW THE LADY WHO EREWHILE APPEARED VEILED UNDERNEATH THE ANGELIC FESTIVAL DIRECT HER EYES TO ME ACROSS THE RIVER", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "98666512432cd49886f7770c6db5febc", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 9.35, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_84-121550-0027", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/84/121550/84-121550-0027.wav", "ref_text": "LOOK AT ME WELL IN SOOTH I'M BEATRICE", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "23a018afe92cacc49a56469dc3b9ef85", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 3.995, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_84-121550-0028", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/84/121550/84-121550-0028.wav", "ref_text": "YE KEEP YOUR WATCH IN THE ETERNAL DAY SO THAT NOR NIGHT NOR SLEEP CAN STEAL FROM YOU ONE STEP THE AGES MAKE UPON THEIR PATH", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "1a2f2c50edd353521d3ddf8d5e350160", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 7.64, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_84-121550-0029", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/84/121550/84-121550-0029.wav", "ref_text": "THEREFORE MY ANSWER IS WITH GREATER CARE THAT HE MAY HEAR ME WHO IS WEEPING YONDER SO THAT THE SIN AND DOLE BE OF ONE MEASURE", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "ddccf697ecb0ed0f8f003c03f7058262", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 8.385, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_84-121550-0030", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/84/121550/84-121550-0030.wav", "ref_text": "BUT BY THE LARGESS OF CELESTIAL GRACES WHICH HAVE SUCH LOFTY VAPOURS FOR THEIR RAIN THAT NEAR TO THEM OUR SIGHT APPROACHES NOT", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "53251a6ad9a378605733621a29cbe96b", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 8.925, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_84-121550-0031", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/84/121550/84-121550-0031.wav", "ref_text": "AS SOON AS EVER OF MY SECOND AGE I WAS UPON THE THRESHOLD AND CHANGED LIFE HIMSELF FROM ME HE TOOK AND GAVE TO OTHERS", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "7683d99978f88ce1877c7deb1593be48", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 8.655, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_84-121550-0032", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/84/121550/84-121550-0032.wav", "ref_text": "SO LOW HE FELL THAT ALL APPLIANCES FOR HIS SALVATION WERE ALREADY SHORT SAVE SHOWING HIM THE PEOPLE OF PERDITION", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "0236210ac890377214625f5ea743be9d", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 8.25, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_84-121550-0033", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/84/121550/84-121550-0033.wav", "ref_text": "CONFUSION AND DISMAY TOGETHER MINGLED FORCED SUCH A YES FROM OUT MY MOUTH THAT SIGHT WAS NEEDFUL TO THE UNDERSTANDING OF IT", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "6bd922c2321b135ad0882b9c1de4c8d7", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 8.02, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_84-121550-0034", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/84/121550/84-121550-0034.wav", "ref_text": "WHENCE SHE TO ME IN THOSE DESIRES OF MINE WHICH LED THEE TO THE LOVING OF THAT GOOD BEYOND WHICH THERE IS NOTHING TO ASPIRE TO", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "cda96151cd8ca72fa97f5657027931ad", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 8.945, "snr_db": null}
{"utt_id": "en_84-121550-0035", "lang": "en", "wav_path": "data/raw/en/wav/LibriSpeech/dev-clean/84/121550/84-121550-0035.wav", "ref_text": "AND WHAT ALLUREMENTS OR WHAT VANTAGES UPON THE FOREHEAD OF THE OTHERS SHOWED THAT THOU SHOULDST TURN THY FOOTSTEPS UNTO THEM", "ref_phon": null, "audio_md5": "db427a26dddd7c2da9764aac1de1f88e", "sr": 16000, "duration_s": 8.22, "snr_db": null}
